    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ終了後の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The night after the live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2099.9999761999998,
          "startTime": 2.0999999762
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5090,
          "startTime": 5.09
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……ん、ビデオ通話？　千紗？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Huh? Video call? From Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.0999999762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 6.8499999762
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 6.8499999762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "こんばんは\n{user}さんは今、事務所ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good evening.\nIs {user}-san at the office right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、残業中だよ\nそっちはライブの打ち上げをしているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ working overtime.\nAre you having the after-party for the live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.1666666429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、みんなでこころちゃんの部屋に集まって\nパジャマパーティーの真っ最中です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ everyone's gathered in Kokoro-chan's room\nand having a pajama party.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.5333333095
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、みんなでカードゲームをしてたんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were playing card games…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5333333095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "私が最下位になっちゃって\n今から罰ゲームをやらなくちゃいけないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and I ended up in last place.\nSo‚ I have to do a punishment game now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.4999999762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "罰ゲームって、何をするんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of punishment game?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4999999762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんに電話して\n普段思ってても言えないことを告白するんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I have to call {user}-san and confess something\nI've been thinking but couldn't say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 45.5333333095
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "だから……思い切って打ち明けるので、聞いて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… I'll spit it out and please listen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5333333095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.4666666429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（普段思ってても言えないことだと？）\n（俺は一体何を言われるんだ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Something I've been thinking but couldn't say?）\n（What is she going to say to me?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 59.3332493469
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと思ってたんですけど……\n{user}さんは働き過ぎだと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been thinking this for a while… {user}-san‚\nI think you're working too much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "また倒れるんじゃないかってみんな心配してます！\nもっと自分の体を大切にして下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone's worried you might collapse again!\nPlease take better care of yourself!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.7999999762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え……あ、わ、分かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… ah‚ I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7999999762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.2666666429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "分かってません！　今日もライブで忙しかったのに\n事務所に戻って残業してるじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't understand! Despite being busy with the live today‚\nyou're back at the office working overtime!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "今夜くらい残業はやめて、早く帰って休んで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please stop overtime tonight and go home early to rest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9333333095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 87.3666666429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……それが、日頃から俺に対して\n思っていたことなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is this what you've been\nthinking about me all this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.7999999762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "他にもあります！　{user}さんは\nなんでも抱え込み過ぎです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's more! {user}-san‚\nyou take on too much by yourself!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3671528883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.6333333095
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとした相談も真剣に聞いてくれて\n忙しいのに時間を作って一緒に悩んでくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even for trivial concerns‚ you listen attentively\nand make time to worry with us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって親身になって私達を支えようとするから\n自分の仕事をする時間がなくなるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because you're so considerate and supportive‚\nyou don't have time for your own work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 113.9333333095
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それはマネージャーとして\n少しでもみんなの力になりたいと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a manager‚\nI just want to be of help to everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4222005328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "分かってます、{user}さんは\nいつもそばにいて私を支えてくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. {user}-san‚\nyou're always there supporting me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがいてくれるから\n私は安心して、思い切り頑張れるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because {user}-san is there‚\nI can give my best with peace of mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 131.8999999762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "だから、しっかり休んで、健康に気を付けて\nこれからもずっと支えて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ please take a good rest and take care of your health‚\nand continue supporting us forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……さっきまで文句を言われる流れだったのに\n途中から俺への不満じゃなくなってるが、いいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I was just being criticized earlier‚\nbut now it's turned into something else. Is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 146.6999999762
    },
